divs: Sighting DetailsI have reported these object previously however tonight the sighting was unique in that there were two witnesses. Up to nine unusually shaped glowing white objects materialized in the eastern sky going at high rate of speed 500mph at least. Objects appeared to witness for up to 10 seconds before fading out. Objects seemed to alter positions in this formation. No noise was heard. I have seen these objects mutiple times
